<h1 class="entry-title"><em>Get gorgeous. <br class="show-for-medium-down" />Get "ooh la la".</em>
Get <em>the best</em> Brazilian wax in Cardiff.</h1>
If you want an on-trend, precision hot wax that leaves no hair standing, you need to get Madame Waxed.

Our reputation for <strong>meticulous detail</strong>, <strong>scrupulous hygiene</strong> and a <strong>razor sharp finish</strong> means smart Cardiff customers rarely trust anywhere else.

Our 30-minute treatment time won't leave you feeling rushed – and it's plenty of time to ensure every last rogue hair is long gone. Plus, our superior quality hot wax and exceptional skill means becoming hair free is pain-free. You get all the <em>"Ooh"</em> without the "Ouch".

You can get a <strong><a href="/top-to-toe-waxing">head to toe wax treatment</a></strong>, but the house speciality is <strong><a href="/brazilian-waxing">the Brazilian</a></strong>. It's THE best in Cardiff and will leave your skin hair free, silky soft and satin smooth – and you'll float out of your treatment oozing with confidence.

We also offer a range of male waxing treatments, taking you from zero to <em>Va Va Voooom</em> in no time at all. Head over to our <strong><a title="Male Waxing" href="http://madamewax.com/male-waxing/">Monsieur Wax menu</a></strong>.

So if you need to sort out down below, trust Madame Wax to leave you feeling amazing.

To get started, check out our Waxing Menus and <a title="How to get Madame Waxed" href="http://madamewax.com/find-us/">opening times</a>, then call us on <strong>(029) 2023 2560 </strong>or <strong><a href="/book-online">book online</a></strong>.

Your body will thank you for it. "Ooh la la!"

